\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
the 95% two-sided confidence interval for 
\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

 consists of those values of d within 
\begin_inset Formula $\pm1.96$
\end_inset

 standard errors of 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{Y}_{m}-\overline{Y}_{w}$
\end_inset

 , thus 
\begin_inset Formula $d=\mu_{m}-\mu_{w}$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(\overline{Y}_{m}-\overline{Y}_{w})\pm1.96SE(\overline{Y}_{m}-\overline{Y}_{w})
\]

\end_inset


